dct_title_s: Particuliere kaerte van de Kusten van Poittou, Aunis En Rochel
dct_alternative_sm: Carte particuliere des costes de Poittou, Aunis, Et De La Rochelle et du fort S.t Louys comme außy de l'Isle de Rè ou S.t Martin avec ses forts
dct_description_sm: 3 bar scales on map, given in "Schale van Vadem" (also "Echelle de toisse"); and "Schale van Mylen" (also "Echelle de lieves").
North oriented toward upper right of sheet.
Index in sea, to the right of insets.
Decorative cartouche with armored figure, compass rose, rhumb lines, buildings, vegetation, ships.
Extensive descriptive text in gothic script at bottom.
French title in cartouche beneath Dutch title; French scale statements on bar scales.
